OL,3,CNewcastle's Eddie Howe urges FA not to
OL,4,C'throw the book' at suspended Tonali
OL,6,FNewcastle United head coach Eddie Howe
OL,7,Fhas said he hopes there are no further
OL,8,Fbans for midfielder Sandro Tonali
OL,9,Ffollowing alleged betting offences.
OL,11,FSpeaking at a press conference ahead
OL,12,Fof the team's match against West Ham
OL,13,Fon Saturday 30 March, Howe urged the
OL,14,FFootball Association not to "throw the
OL,15,Fbook" at the player.
