OL,3,CNewcastle's Eddie Howe urges FA not to
OL,4,C'throw the book' at suspended Tonali
OL,6,FThe charges relate to alleged offences
OL,7,Fcommitted after signing for Newcastle
OL,8,Fin the summer. He is alleged to have
OL,9,Fbreached FA rule E8 50 times by
OL,10,Fbetting on matches between 12 August
OL,11,F2023 and 12 October 2023.
OL,13,FThe 23-year-old is currently serving a
OL,14,Fseparate ten-month suspension from the
OL,15,FItalian Football Federation (FIGC) for
OL,16,Fbetting offences committed during his
OL,17,Ftime with AC Milan.
OL,19,FTonali has until 5 April to respond to
OL,20,Fthe latest charges.
