OL,3,CNewcastle's Eddie Howe urges FA not to
OL,4,C'throw the book' at suspended Tonali
OL,6,FHowe said: "The news that there was an
OL,7,FFA charge, that illness didn't stop
OL,8,Fwhen he moved from Italy to England,
OL,9,Fthat illness was there and people
OL,10,Fshould look at it that way, not 'let's
OL,11,Fthrow the book at him and let's punish
OL,12,Fhim even further' because I don't
OL,13,Fthink that gets to the root of the
OL,14,Fproblem.
OL,16,F"We need to protect all our players
OL,17,Fbecause this is something that's open
OL,18,Fto everybody and becoming a bigger
OL,19,Fproblem in society, so this isn't just
OL,20,Fa problem for Sandro."
