OL,3,CNewcastle's Eddie Howe urges FA not to
OL,4,C'throw the book' at suspended Tonali
OL,6,FTonali's initial 18-month suspension
OL,7,Fwas reduced by eight months on
OL,8,Fcondition that he underwent treatment
OL,9,Ffor his addiction. He was also made to
OL,10,Ftalk to young players in Italy on at
OL,11,Fleast 16 occasions about the dangers
OL,12,Fof gambling.
OL,14,FWhile serving his worldwide ban,
OL,15,FTonali is still allowed to train with
OL,16,FNewcastle, but cannot play again until
OL,17,Fthe end of August.
