OL,3,CNewcastle's Eddie Howe urges FA not to
OL,4,C'throw the book' at suspended Tonali
OL,6,FAccording to Howe, Tonali is "seeking
OL,7,Fhelp on a regular basis. This is
OL,8,Fsomething that won't go away for him,
OL,9,Fso he has regular meetings in Italy
OL,10,Fand in England to deal with the
OL,11,Fproblems that he has.
OL,13,F"But I have to say mentally, he's been
OL,14,Fvery good in his training sessions,
OL,15,Fhe's been very good off the pitch.
OL,16,FHe's been a brilliant team-mate to the
OL,17,Fpeople here and supporting team-mates
OL,18,Fand training really well to set a
OL,19,Fpositive example.
