OL,3,CNewcastle's Eddie Howe urges FA not to
OL,4,C'throw the book' at suspended Tonali
OL,6,F"His English has improved a lot as
OL,7,Fwell, which has been great. He can
OL,8,Fcommunicate now really well with his
OL,9,Fteam-mates, which is such an important
OL,10,Fthing.
OL,12,F"I'm really positive about his
OL,13,Fcomeback, whenever that is, that he'll
OL,14,Fhave a huge impact on the team."
